StatementHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: BY variables ;

A BY statement can be used with PROC GANTT to obtain separate Gantt charts for 
observations in groups defined by the BY variables.

StatementOptionHelp.#cdata:
[Syntax: HMILE=height] 

Specifies the height in cells of the milestone symbol. The height is a positive real number; 
the default value is 1.0.
